Malabar Gold and Diamonds, unveils an exclusive
brand “Mine” which is a joint venture between
Mahendra Brothers (One of the World’s first & largest
DTC Sight-holders from India) and Malabar gold &
Diamonds (The Leading Retail Jewellery Chain).
Our captivating “Mine” brand offers an exotic &
exquisite range of varied diamond jewellery which
includes pristine Bridal, Solitaire, Casual jewellery
collection beautifully crafted in yellow gold, white gold
and platinum metal in innovative and the best of
designs. Our Mine diamond collection inspires all
jewellery lovers and accentuates the true beauty and
essence of a women. And, for all the stylish men out
there, we have minimalistic diamond jewellery for men
that will undoubtedly complement his charismatic
personality.
